Model.Text: Thank you everyone for finding what I've misplaced.
I truly hope you all enjoyed yourself during the search.
So what the heck did you want us to find this skull for!?
Well as per our little agreement, the doors shall be opened.
Allow me to bestow upon you these treasures, to show my appreciation.
Take care now... and have a nice life.
When you come to, you find that what was originally a thriving, grand mansion, has become a dilapidated, abandoned shell.
As if no one had lived there for many, many years.
And not a trace remains of Jack, the night's host...
Opening the box Jack gave you, you find it packed full with a myriad of riches.
And at that moment, you find your mind the host of a terrifying thought...
What if Jack Stinchy... was this mansion's former owner?
And his spirit had been roaming its crumbling halls for all these years, just waiting for someone to find his missing skull?
The possibility sends shivers down your spine...
You brush the thought off as insane, impossible, but can't shake off the eerie feeling it's left you.
You try to tell yourself that what happened tonight,
was nothing but a bad dream, or some cloying hallucination...
